cat << EOF
FbDesk is a fluxbox-util application that creates and manage icons on your
Fluxbox desktop.

Implemented Features:

    * XPM and PNG image loading
    * Antialias text
    * UTF-8 and multibyte support
    * Vertical text
    * Grid Snapping
    * GUI for editing command/label and add/remove icons
    * Fluxbox menu style
EOF
